network_nodes.ERK: MEK AND NOT afatinib AND NOT gefitinib AND NOT dacomitinib
network_nodes.JNK: MEK AND NOT afatinib AND NOT gefitinib AND NOT dacomitinib
network_nodes.RalGDS: KRAS AND NOT berberine AND NOT gefitinib
network_nodes.GLI1: (ERK AND NOT berberine AND NOT gefitinib AND NOT afatinib AND NOT palmatine) OR SMAD
network_nodes.IKK: PKBAKT AND NOT palmatine AND NOT berberine AND NOT gefitinib AND NOT dacomitinib AND NOT afatinib
network_nodes.TSC1by2: (NOT PKBAKT AND NOT palmatine AND NOT berberine AND NOT gefitinib AND NOT dacomitinib AND NOT afatinib AND AMPK) OR berberine
network_nodes.RPS6KB: (mTOR AND NOT berberine) OR (ERK AND NOT berberine AND NOT gefitinib AND NOT afatinib AND NOT palmatine) OR PDPK
network_nodes.BAD: NOT PKBAKT AND NOT palmatine AND NOT berberine AND NOT gefitinib AND NOT dacomitinib AND NOT afatinib AND NOT RPS6KB

output_nodes.SP1: ERK AND NOT berberine AND NOT gefitinib AND NOT afatinib AND NOT palmatine
output_nodes.BAX: (P53 OR gemcitabine) AND NOT BCLXL AND NOT abraxane AND NOT GANT61
